Object-oriented language, good for Windows apps and Unity games, cleaner than C++ but less low-level

Common type sizes:

| Type | Size |
| --- | --- |
| bool | 1 byte |
| byte / sbyte | 1 byte |
| char | 2 bytes |
| short / ushort | 2 bytes |
| int / uint | 4 bytes |
| long / ulong | 8 bytes |
| nint / nuint | 4 bytes on 32-bit systems, 8 bytes on 64-bit systems |
| float | 4 bytes |
| double | 8 bytes |
| decimal | 16 bytes |
